✅ Main Features
🧑‍🏫 For Lecturers:
Login / Register

Generate QR Code per class/session (with session title/name)

QR Refreshes every 3 minutes automatically for security

View Dashboard:

List of all past QR sessions

For each QR session: view attendance (name, index number, phone, GPS location, time of scan)

🎓 For Students:
Login / Register

Update Bio Data (name, index number, phone number)

Scan QR Code

On scan: app captures their info + current GPS location and submits it to the backend

🧰 Tech Stack
Layer Tech
Frontend Vite + React + TypeScript
UI Bootstrap CSS
ShadCN
Backend Node.js + Express
Auth JWT Authentication
Database MongoDB
QR Scanning Browser API / QR scanner lib
GPS Browser Geolocation API
Socket.io

Student dashboard;

